Description
A digital repack of some Ant-Man stories to whet your appetite for the new Ant-Man movie. Not a complete torrent unless you want to overload on, like, every Avengers comic, ever.

This torrent has the origins of the Astonishing Ant-Man, Henry Pym, weighted with more Scott Lang stories. Also includes the Annoying Ant-Man, Eric O'Grady.

I've tried to include complete(ish) storylines involving the character wherever possible. Ant-Man was often thrown into the middle of things.

Of particular note is Marvel Team-Up 103, featuring a shoutout to ROM Spaceknight on the third panel of page two. Because I like that kinda thing.
